com.blazegraph.gremlin.structure

Interface BlazeElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BlazeReifiedElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlazeEdge, BlazeVertex, BlazeVertexProperty, EmptyBlazeVertexProperty

    public interface BlazeElement
extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element
    Extends the Tinkerpop3 interface to strengthen return types from Iterator to CloseableIterator and to expose RDF values for id and label.
    Author:
    mikepersonick
